'''Mouloudia Club of Oujda''' ({{lang-ar|مولودية وجدة}}) is a Moroccan [[football (soccer)|football]] club based in [[Oujda]]. Mouloudia, which closely translates to "birth" in  Arabic, was named after the coincidence of the day of its creation: on March 16, 1946 (12 second spring of 1365 Hjeria) with the anniversary of the birth of [[Muhammad]].

